flowchart TD
  A[User input: text audio image crop batch sequence] --> B[Build intake payload]
  B --> C[Validate media policy and workspace]
  C -->|invalid| D[Blocked: no files written]
  C -->|valid| E{Spec target}
  E -->|none| F[Save as ordinary feedback]
  E -->|new_spec| G[Dry-run new spec plan]
  E -->|existing_spec| H[Validate spec id and artifact]
  H -->|invalid| D
  G -->|collision or unsafe| D
  G -->|safe| I[Create intake package and spec skeleton]
  H -->|safe| J[Create edit job]
  I --> K[Prepare context pack]
  J --> K
  K --> L[Run Codex CLI in target repo]
  L -->|failed cancelled timeout| M[Preserve intake and expose next actions]
  L -->|success| N[Apply reviewed output]
  N --> O[Refresh metadata traceability indexes]
  O --> P[Workbench shows updated spec state]
